CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper November 6, 1965, pg. 24, reads: "Powerful Aggregation - Here is the powerful Westinghouse High School football team, unbeaten and once again favored to win the Pittsburgh City League arid championship.  Left to right, back row, Wesley Garnett, Gregory Vasser, Hawthorne Conley, Wade Lipscomb and Ernest Whitted.  Front row, from left: Eugene Harrison, Lloyd Weston, Marshall Ellison, Cyphus Alston, Dorian Vasser, Richard [illegible] ... The team, which has won [illegible] ... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Westinghouse High School football players, including Wesley Garnett, Gregory Vasser, Hawthorne Conley, Wade Lipscomb, Ernest Whitted, Eugene Harrison, Lloyd Weston, Marshall Ellison, Cyphus Alston, Dorian Vasser, Richard, and unknown players
